title: 2 Bedroom Apartment Home Available at Woodway Village. Call NOW!
posting_body: ['Welcome to better living.', 'Welcome to Woodway Village Apartments.', 'Our 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment homes and townhouses include large bedrooms with ample closet space, central air-conditioning, fully equipped kitchens & an attached garage with EVERY HOME!', 'Located just a short drive from Downtown Austin, near many dining, shopping, and entertainment options right outside of your front door.', 'Our community offers a sparkling outdoor pool, picnic & BBQ areas, on-site daycare, and an outdoor playground & dog park!', 'At Woodway Village, we take care of our residents.', 'If you would like to learn more, make sure you call soon and schedule your tour.', 'TRANSFORMATION UNDERWAY - RENOVATION IN PROGRESS!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Gated Controlled Entry Access System', '- Updated Kitchen & Bathroom Cabinetry', '- 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance Service', '- Walk-In Closet(s)', '- Located Along IH-35', 'Corridor - Just a Few Minutes from Downtown Austin', '- Pet-Friendly Community', '- Exterior Lighting Package', '- Laundry Facility', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Woodway Village participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $46,380 | 2 Occupants: $52,980 | 3', 'Occupants: $59,580 | 4 Occupants: $66,180 | 5 Occupants: $71,520 | 6 Occupants: $76,800.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community;\xa0credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Tuesday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Thursday-Friday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to learn more about our community:', 'show contact info', 'Woodway Village', '4600 Nuckols Crossing Road', 'Austin, TX, 78744', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'zB0ZM9weOf8']
